Name: Brain Works
Services Offered: Day Care Centres , Preschools ,
Details:
Brain Works is a national chain of preschools that provides a world class learning environment and scientifically researched curriculum to maximize development of children during the early childhood years. Brain Works believes in providing a rich, stimulating environment using an eclectic approach geared to match different learning styles in children and recent research on brain development.The preschool follows a brain based learning methodology whereby regular stimulation is given to a child during the "windows of opportunity" which are the critical periods in a child's life when specific learning takes place. They also believe in creating an environment which encourages learning with all the five senses through which an infant's social, emotional, cognitive, physical and language development are stimulated during multi-sensory experiences.Brain research within a nurturing environment is one of the main goals of Brain Works. The organization strives to enable children to develop their social, emotional, physical and academic skills resulting in a joy towards learning. Brain Works also aims to make parent participation an integral part of their academic programme and to make each parent more knowledgeable about child development, behavior patterns and positive guidance techniques.Our Vision:
At Brain Works, we aspire to be a leading provider of 'high-quality and affordable' preschool / day-care services, which allow children to realize their potential. Our diverse methods based on brain research help provide a child a head-start in life.
Our Mission:Maximising the "Windows of opportunity" to enhance learning and maximizing development of the brain in children aged 0-6 years through a scientifically research driven teaching and learning environment encouraging the natural qualities of creativity, curiosity and eagerness to learn in children to develop to their fullest potential.If you want to know more about our services, just let us know about it. We will certainly get back to you as soon as we received your query.
